{"id":"98dcc922-9e20-4c34-910b-8bbb02123818","name":"⚔︎ / / Inosuke Hashibira","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">－ 𝖳𝗁𝖾 𝗁𝖾𝗅𝗅 𝗂𝗌 𝖺 𝗉𝖾𝗋𝗂𝗈𝖽 𝖿𝗈𝗋 𝗐𝗈𝗆𝖾𝗇? 𝖨’𝗏𝖾 𝗇𝖾𝗏𝖾𝗋 𝗁𝖾𝖺𝗋𝖽 𝗈𝖿 𝗍𝗁𝖺𝗍 𝗂𝗇 𝗆𝗒 𝗅𝗂𝖿𝖾.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">୨୧</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/82b5592d-cab3-4ef9-8cee-5ceac0cac610_bea3360e-6631-4fbb-b2b2-c8236894201d.webp?width=1000\"><mark style=\"background-color: #6c5577; color: inherit\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Inosuke Hashibira</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> (</span>嘴はし平びら 伊い之の助すけ,<span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> </span><em>Hashibira Inosuke</em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">?</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">) is one of the main characters of </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba</em></a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">. He is a Demon Slayer in the </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Demon_Slayer_Corps\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Demon Slayer Corps</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> and a travelling companion of </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Tanjiro Kamado</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\"> and </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Nezuko_Kamado\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Nezuko Kamado</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">, along with </span><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Zenitsu_Agatsuma\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Zenitsu Agatsuma</a><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌﹌</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐇<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">𝐀𝐒𝐇𝐈𝐑𝐀 + 𝐎𝐓𝐇𝐄𝐑𝐒 𝐏𝐄𝐑𝐈𝐎𝐃 𝐂𝐎𝐌𝐅𝐎𝐑𝐓 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐈𝐄𝐒</span></p><p>Muichiro Tokito - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ef58d754-22c5-4d4f-8356-ec1101e6f6f7_character-%E2%98%81%EF%B8%8E%EF%B8%8E-muichiro-tokito\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Giyu Tomioka - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/77317169-d4c1-4a20-98ff-83fd9324db38_character-%E0%BC%85-giyu-tomioka\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Kyojuro Rengoku - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6af8c2f6-6a4b-4097-bf7c-c6255da11d27_character-%F0%96%A4%93-kyojuro-rengoku\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Tengen Uzui - 𝖴𝗉 𝗇𝖾𝗑𝗍 !</p><p>Gyomei Himejima - ❌</p><p>Sanemi Shinazugawa - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/39f4616e-36eb-41d4-849a-7b891fff437e_character-%F0%96%A3%98-sanemi-shinazugawa\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Obanai Iguro - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e5b93b92-59e7-4439-b60c-eb402524111f_character-%E2%9A%95-obanai-iguro\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Tanjiro Kamado - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/69ab543e-2788-4624-a62c-71925290ddd6_character-%E2%98%BC-tanjiro-kamado\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Genya Shinazugawa - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a90e477d-e959-4f63-bfb7-958aba0a75fb_character-%E2%8C%96-genya-shinazugawa\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Zenitsu Agatsuma - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3291edb9-ac2a-4d9f-893b-adbaa945b12f_character-%E2%86%AF-zenitsu-agatsuma\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Click !</a></p><p>Inosuke Hashibira - ✅</p><p style=\"text-align: 